data.description:
Lovely lot with a spring fed pond and stream, offering privacy and convenience only 5 minutes and 1.6 miles from downtown Saluda. 
Home has beautiful wooden cabinets and ceiling with much potential for good living. Currently the property is 
being cleared of debris and equipment.  Property is being sold 'as is'. This is a great opportunity for investors or folks looking to live in Saluda.  With many years as a family home, it has been lovingly adorned with artisan woodwork. 
Property can be subdivided into 2 lots!!!
Saluda is a destination for biking, hiking, dining, kayaking and the enjoyment of the many natural wonders of Western North Carolina.  Come see it for yourself to discover if it is a right fit for you!
Listing agent will accompany any showings
